Dependencies

For convenience the dependencies are shipped in the zip distribution but they belong to the following organizations and their licenses must be considered at all times.

Apache Jena

The following from the Apache Jena project at http://jena.apache.org/ . License :


  • jena-arq-2.11.1.jar
  • jena-core-2.11.1.jar
  • jena-iri-1.0.1.jar


Download from http://jena.apache.org/download/index.cgi .

SL4J

The following from the Simple Logging Facade for Java project at http://www.slf4j.org/ . License

  • slf4j-api-1.6.4.jar
  • jcl-over-slf4j-1.6.4.jar
  • slf4j-log4j12-1.6.4.jar

Download from http://www.slf4j.org/download.html .

Apache Log4J

The following from the Log4J project at http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/ . License :

  • log4j-1.2.16.jar

Download from http://logging.apache.org/log4j/1.2/download.html .

Apache Xerces

The following from the Apache Xerces project at http://xerces.apache.org/ . License :


  • xercesImpl-2.11.0.jar
  • xml-apis-1.4.01.jar


Download from http://xerces.apache.org/mirrors.cgi .


Remember to always check your download authenticity. Including ours!
